{"tid":1631542,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"「小急」有無巴絲知道圖中位置？","createTime":"2019-10-06T15:45:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-10T04:54:45.000Z","uid":120214,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"ed87ae85b9c14f63cc67637b466f9aa16c2be40f","tid":1631542,"uid":120214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:45:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/n4ibdJk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fn4ibdJk.jpg&h=764a01d6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n事原係因為有支那狗話 圖中西人繪畫係因為要消除運動字句。但我覺得好假，希望各位幫幫手FC<br />\n<br />\n依單嘢已經在台灣流傳，有部分台灣人立場開始動搖"},{"pid":"ea3004307f50cb4be3733a2d7e8d0d26de9a9ef1","tid":1631542,"uid":130079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:46:00.000Z","msg":"［眾籌俾連登］開一個英文版面俾連登仔<br />\n【重開】［眾籌俾連登］開一個英文版面俾連登仔<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1630849\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1630849</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1630201\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1630201</a><br />\n<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n現時連登急需亦好要一個<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">英文台/或者係新既英文介面，全部台都有英文版咁。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n主要用途係對外文宣用，如果個論壇冧左，<span style=\"color: purple;\">外國人更加清楚lihkg被攻擊同香港自由被剝既嚴重性</span>。<br />\n<br />\ntwitter有lihkg,reddit開post<br />\n但始終都唔係lihkg開英文台<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好處：<br />\n1.連登多左流覽量，廣告費多左<br />\n2.同上，每次被攻擊都睇到香港無自由，the world is watching<br />\n3.理論上少風向文宣，因為如果要落手帶風向，對家就要大學畢業既人，文宣戰立即少左散仔協會參戰，但香港市民最多就係呢一堆人。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家如果見到既<br />\n幫手：<br />\n1.<span style=\"color: red;\">幫推，唔該3連推一次</span><br />\n2.連登search其他 英文台 國際台，<span style=\"color: green;\">將入面相關要求既post再推</span><br />\n<br />\n3.share link去fb tg，叫其他有account既人入黎再一齊做返1同2<br />\n4.<span style=\"color: orange;\">堅持每日全部post再一推</span><br />\n5.Fb 連登到留comment，叫連仔開英文台<br />\n6. Fb進行洗版式接龍活動，令到連仔開到/知道要開英文台為止<br />\n7.太舊既post只可以推番三個上水，幫手推埋thx<br />\n<br />\n如果你係要求開英文台post樓主既：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">集中連推自己所有既英文台post，我會幫推，唔好放棄推<br />\n</span></span>"},{"pid":"ae6c04040aceb2e1656cc6b928b4f03fca32245a","tid":1631542,"uid":75425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:50:52.000Z","msg":"有d似紅磡天橋舊時新個頭"},{"pid":"706dd882016047797ba6c707cd8e25dc8addf04e","tid":1631542,"uid":120214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ae6c04040aceb2e1656cc6b928b4f03fca32245a","tid":1631542,"uid":75425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:50:52.000Z","msg":"有d似紅磡天橋舊時新個頭"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:52:24.000Z","msg":"開google map 睇下先"},{"pid":"0edc01c847ea432e43558841fce3db62dec87cc9","tid":1631542,"uid":120214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ae6c04040aceb2e1656cc6b928b4f03fca32245a","tid":1631542,"uid":75425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:50:52.000Z","msg":"有d似紅磡天橋舊時新個頭"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:56:00.000Z","msg":"巴打，有冇準確位置？"},{"pid":"e0b8b975266ad255d33c2c2a763265815d4921f1","tid":1631542,"uid":75425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0edc01c847ea432e43558841fce3db62dec87cc9","tid":1631542,"uid":120214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ae6c04040aceb2e1656cc6b928b4f03fca32245a","tid":1631542,"uid":75425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:50:52.000Z","msg":"有d似紅磡天橋舊時新個頭"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:56:00.000Z","msg":"巴打，有冇準確位置？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:03:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/03CrNaG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F03CrNaG.png&h=30c69ea1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我聽日去睇睇"},{"pid":"a67d88af88e9bceabe8133f73f655ec277b00574","tid":1631542,"uid":71824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ae6c04040aceb2e1656cc6b928b4f03fca32245a","tid":1631542,"uid":75425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:50:52.000Z","ms